---
export const prerender = true;
import PublicLayout from '@/layouts/PublicLayout.astro';

---

<PublicLayout
  title="Terms of Use — Springbok Expeditions"
  description="Springbok Expeditions website terms of use."
>
  <section class="section bg-dusk-50">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow text-safari-600 mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-display-sm md:text-display-md font-display font-medium tracking-tight text-safari-900 mb-4">
        Terms of Use
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-dusk-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-dusk-100 p-8 md:p-10 space-y-8 text-dusk-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          These terms govern your use of the Springbok Expeditions website (springbokexpeditions.com). By using the site, you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, please don't use the site.
        </p>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
          <p>Springbok Expeditions is a tour operator based in Arusha, Tanzania. References to "we", "us", "our", or "Springbok" mean Springbok Expeditions.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">2. Use of the website</h2>
          <p>You may use this website to browse our tours, request a quote, and book a trip. You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Use the site for any unlawful purpose</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the site</li>
            <li>Copy, scrape, or republish our content (including tour descriptions and images) without written permission</li>
            <li>Submit false or misleading information through our forms</li>
            <li>Interfere with the site's operation or security</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">3. Content</h2>
          <p>All content on this site — including text, photographs, itineraries, prices, and design — is owned by Springbok Expeditions or our licensors. It is provided for your personal, non-commercial use. Pricing and availability are indicative until confirmed in a written quote.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">4. Quotes and bookings</h2>
          <p>A quote we send you is valid for 30 days unless otherwise noted. A booking is confirmed only when we receive your deposit and send a written confirmation. Trip-specific terms (payment schedule, cancellation, inclusions) are set out in our booking conditions.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">5. Third-party links</h2>
          <p>We sometimes link to third-party sites (airlines, hotels, visa services). We don't control those sites and aren't responsible for their content or practices.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">6. Liability</h2>
          <p>We work hard to keep the site accurate and available, but we don't guarantee that it will be error-free or uninterrupted. To the maximum extent permitted by law, we exclude liability for any indirect or consequential losses arising from your use of the site.</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Nothing in these terms excludes liability for fraud, death, or personal injury caused by negligence.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">7. Governing law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the United Republic of Tanzania. Any disputes will be handled by the courts of Tanzania, unless required otherwise by mandatory consumer law in your home country.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:info@springbokexpeditions.com" class="text-safari-700 underline hover:text-safari-900">info@springbokexpeditions.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
